sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Your Machine<br/>(Claude CLI)
    participant API as Anthropic API<br/>(api.anthropic.com)
    participant Target as Target Website<br/>(example.com)

    User->>API: POST /v1/messages (prompt + conversation)

    Note over API: API server fetches on your behalf

    API->>Target: GET https://example.com
    Target-->>API: 200 OK (page content)

    Note over API: Target server sees ANTHROPIC's IP address
    Note over API: Anthropic can read the fetched content

    API-->>User: Response: summary of the page
